The following pages describe ways to insert and update dates and times in buffers and files:

* TimeStamp -- Automatically insert and update dates and times in buffers and files.
* InsertingTodaysDate -- quickly insert the current date in things like articles, letters and other written documents.
* InsertDate -- insert the current date in various formats depending on the prefix argument
* InsertAnyDate -- a way to quickly insert a date other than the current date.

